---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

import '../../styles/global.css';

// Importing SEO data for the About page
import seoData from '@/data/js/services/gmpComplianceTrainings';
---

<Layout
  seo={{
    title: `${seoData.meta.title} - Indivirtus`,
    description: seoData.meta.description,
    keywords: seoData.meta.keywords,
    canonical: seoData.meta.canonicalUrl,
    image: seoData.image.path.src,
    url: seoData.pageLink,
    schema: seoData.schema,
  }}
>
  <article class="maxwidth px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="bg-primary-light mb-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r px-6 py-16 text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold">GMP Compliance & Workforce Excellence</h1>
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-semibold">For Pharmaceutical & Biotech Organizations</h2>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-lg opacity-90">
          Transform your quality systems with our comprehensive training, SOP development, and compliance auditing
          services tailored to Schedule M and global GMP standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="mb-16 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p>
          In today's highly regulated pharmaceutical environment, maintaining <strong>GMP compliance</strong> while fostering
          a <strong>quality culture</strong> is non-negotiable. Our specialized services bridge the gap between regulatory
          requirements and practical implementation through:
        </p>

        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
          <li><strong>Workforce training programs</strong> that build sustainable compliance competencies</li>
          <li><strong>SOP systems</strong> that reflect both regulatory expectations and operational realities</li>
          <li><strong>Implementation support</strong> that ensures sustainable quality systems</li>
          <li><strong>Compliance audits</strong> aligned with Schedule M, WHO-GMP, and 21 CFR Part 210/211</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-6">
          We go beyond documentation to create <strong>inspection-ready organizations</strong> where quality is embedded
          in daily operations rather than treated as a compliance exercise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800">Our GMP Compliance Solutions</h2>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Training -->
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
          <div
            class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 transition-colors group-hover:bg-blue-200"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">GMP Workforce Training</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-gray-700">
            <li>Role-specific competency development</li>
            <li>Data integrity awareness programs</li>
            <li>Train-the-trainer initiatives</li>
            <li>Behavioral quality training</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- SOP Development -->
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
          <div
            class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 transition-colors group-hover:bg-green-200"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-green-700">SOP Development</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-gray-700">
            <li>Regulatory-aligned documentation</li>
            <li>Process-specific SOP frameworks</li>
            <li>Controlled document systems</li>
            <li>Electronic SOP implementation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Implementation -->
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
          <div
            class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-purple-100 transition-colors group-hover:bg-purple-200"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"
              ></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-purple-700">Implementation Support</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-gray-700">
            <li>Change management strategies</li>
            <li>Process harmonization</li>
            <li>Quality system integration</li>
            <li>SOP rollout planning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Audits -->
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
          <div
            class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 transition-colors group-hover:bg-red-200"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-red-700">Compliance Audits</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-gray-700">
            <li>Schedule M gap assessments</li>
            <li>Mock FDA/MHRA inspections</li>
            <li>Data integrity audits</li>
            <li>Vendor quality evaluations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Quality Culture -->
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
          <div
            class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-yellow-100 transition-colors group-hover:bg-yellow-200"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-700">Quality Culture</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-gray-700">
            <li>Leadership engagement programs</li>
            <li>Quality metrics dashboards</li>
            <li>Behavioral quality interventions</li>
            <li>Continuous improvement frameworks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Inspection -->
        <div class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
          <div
            class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cyan-100 transition-colors group-hover:bg-cyan-200"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-700">Inspection Readiness</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-gray-700">
            <li>Backroom preparation</li>
            <li>Document retrieval systems</li>
            <li>Staff interview coaching</li>
            <li>Response protocol development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Approach Section -->
    <section class="mb-16 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 p-8">
      <h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800">Our Methodology</h2>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">Assessment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We begin with a comprehensive evaluation of your current quality systems against regulatory expectations and
            industry benchmarks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">Customization</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Solutions are tailored to your specific products, processes, and organizational cultureâ€”no generic
            templates.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">Implementation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We provide hands-on support to embed new systems and behaviors, not just deliver documentation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">Verification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Effectiveness is measured through competency assessments, process metrics, and mock inspections.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">Sustainment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We establish mechanisms to maintain compliance momentum through coaching and periodic reviews.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">Continuous Improvement</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Regular updates ensure your systems evolve with changing regulations and business needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits Section -->
    <section class="bg-primary-light mb-16 rounded-xl p-12 text-white">
      <h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-3xl font-bold">Why Partner With Us?</h2>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mt-1 mr-3 h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Regulatory Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100">
              Our team includes former regulators and seasoned quality professionals with deep knowledge of Schedule M,
              WHO-GMP, and FDA requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mt-1 mr-3 h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Practical Implementation</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100">
              We focus on creating systems that work in your real-world environment, not just on paper compliance.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mt-1 mr-3 h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Sustainable Results</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100">
              Our approach builds internal capabilities rather than creating dependency on consultants.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg
            class="mt-1 mr-3 h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-green-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Risk Reduction</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100">Proactive gap identification and remediation minimizes regulatory exposure.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="mb-16 text-center">
      <div class="bg-primary-light inline-block max-w-2xl rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r p-8 text-white shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Ready to Transform Your Compliance Culture?</h3>
        <p class="mb-6 text-lg opacity-90">
          Our GMP experts will help you build inspection-ready quality systems that stand up to regulatory scrutiny.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="/contact-us" class="button"> Schedule Consultation </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
